text.tspan: Associate Design Editor - Collaborate with the Design Director, and

layouts for the short stories. Convert and build print stories for iPad.

and Graphic editors to produce information graphics, art, maps and
layouts for stories. Assist with large projects, implementing changes
from editors and designers and assuring quality control. Convert and
prepare graphics for e-publishing formats and web.
